{"tid":1035812,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"就黎兩個月","createTime":"2019-02-24T19:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T00:09:06.000Z","uid":11110,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd7d3a6f077e90b59906e7883cf2de211164a1e","tid":1035812,"uid":11110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T19:56:37.000Z","msg":"睇理科太太話 人係需要三個月黎reset大腦<br />\n好讓自己可以習慣失戀既痛楚<br />\n<br />\n已經兩個月<br />\n<br />\n但其實我個心仲係想自虐<br />\n想佢一直留係我個心<br />\n想一直鐘意佢<br />\n我先走唔甩<br />\n<br />\n我好明白<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/t0EG6pSwcBk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft0EG6pSwcBk&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=067edabc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t0EG6pSwcBk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">欲斷難斷在<br />\n不甘心去捨割</span><br />\n<br />\n真係好蠢"},{"pid":"7745393a8ea1fee9ab4c847eaa477a4f6c24390f","tid":1035812,"uid":214363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:01:06.000Z","msg":"其實呢d時候 先唔應該走去聽應景既歌"},{"pid":"6d064f978f1f0f0b4e1b6487f25293aab8618ff3","tid":1035812,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrDe37.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrDe37.gif&h=1756b2b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1faafc16c97717c739f1bf1e539be67de4e42d60","tid":1035812,"uid":11110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:01:42.000Z","msg":"亦都唔知係邊度睇到話<br />\n想分開後冇咁傷<br />\n最好最快既方法係憎左前度<br />\n<br />\n我其實呢個月最有進步既係終於識得嬲<br />\n有一日喊左好耐<br />\n突然覺得自己好可憐<br />\n<br />\n要有囡又不停溝我既又係佢<br />\n等我跌晒落坑連最後一根稻草都捉唔住上唔返岸果時先話唔要我<br />\n<br />\n我好痛恨鐘意左佢既自己<br />\n<br />\n我每日都後悔緊<br />\n如果可以同佢做一世既朋友<br />\n我就唔洗咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\n佢擁有晒<br />\n但我咩都冇晒<br />\n<br />\n雖然我開始識嬲<br />\n但我都覺得係冇辦法既事<br />\n<br />\n我都係會原諒到佢<br />\n<br />\n或者可能係<br />\n唔原諒佢<br />\n我都原諒唔到搞鳩人地男朋友既自己"},{"pid":"07398984a675965559defa3213d1e31445a85029","tid":1035812,"uid":11110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7745393a8ea1fee9ab4c847eaa477a4f6c24390f","tid":1035812,"uid":214363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:01:06.000Z","msg":"其實呢d時候 先唔應該走去聽應景既歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:02:32.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n成日都自虐成狂⋯⋯"},{"pid":"33f05bf02e45b5d2ce77ac8100df79071ace4d8f","tid":1035812,"uid":11110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:04:20.000Z","msg":"今日先知未畢到業既佢<br />\n都打算影畢業相<br />\n<br />\n唔同我講係咪連回憶既一小部分都唔留比我？⋯⋯<br />\n好掛住佢⋯"},{"pid":"b734497c0b9a3815c67d87583b24dc72467a0263","tid":1035812,"uid":214363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33f05bf02e45b5d2ce77ac8100df79071ace4d8f","tid":1035812,"uid":11110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:04:20.000Z","msg":"今日先知未畢到業既佢<br />\n都打算影畢業相<br />\n<br />\n唔同我講係咪連回憶既一小部分都唔留比我？⋯⋯<br />\n好掛住佢⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:06:14.000Z","msg":"希望你可以快d痛到麻木 遲d就會發覺呢種病根本係微不足道"},{"pid":"05515ca4908a6fc01fa790552d55c6b4a6218156","tid":1035812,"uid":214363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:08:38.000Z","msg":"當你發覺佢冇左你都可以活得好開心既時候 <br />\n你就應該諗下 <br />\n自己冇左佢<br />\n點樣都可以活得開心"},{"pid":"92eee42ec6b49bb386ef770b39c517f81929b84e","tid":1035812,"uid":11110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05515ca4908a6fc01fa790552d55c6b4a6218156","tid":1035812,"uid":214363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:08:38.000Z","msg":"當你發覺佢冇左你都可以活得好開心既時候 <br />\n你就應該諗下 <br />\n自己冇左佢<br />\n點樣都可以活得開心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:11:37.000Z","msg":"其實我一向都覺得冇男人<br />\n冇佢 我一樣可以好開心<br />\n但只係都係好想要佢⋯<br />\n<br />\nAnyway thanks巴打<br />\n我會努力過每一日<br />\n<br />\n我想做到努力過每一日<br />\n而唔係有時傷春悲秋又浪費左極多時間"},{"pid":"a2764053d09feed7f1a70f225e12d9d89ee3c71b","tid":1035812,"uid":79278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T20:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\